headline: Gartner (IT) Valuation Check As AI Disruption Concerns And Recent Weak Quarter Weigh On Sentiment
summary: Recent commentary around Gartner (IT) has focused on how artificial intelligence may be cutting into demand for its research services, with Jim Cramer highlighting the stock’s sharp 2025 underperformance and a recent quarter he described as disappointing.
